summary: An ordinance relating to zoning and providing for the rezoning of Lots 1, 2, 3, 4 and 5, except the westerly 105 feet thereof, Block 8, Homewood Park Addition, together with the westerly one-half of the vacated alley adjacent to the south one-half of said Lot 3 and said Lots 4 and 5, all situated south of East 123rd Street, between 28th Avenue Northeast and Bothell Way, with respect to Use and Area Districts, and amending Ordinance No. 45382, as amended by adding thereto the two new sections numbered 2-412 and 17-303, respectively.
